				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the curator of the TED conferences, see <a href="Chris_Anderson_(entrepreneur)" title="Chris Anderson (entrepreneur)">Chris Anderson (entrepreneur)</a>.</div>
